Usage: set_path_adjust_group [-help] -name <path_adjust_group_name>
                             [-through <through_list>] [-from <from_list> ] [-to <to_list> ]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-from <from_list>                  # List of pins, instances, or clocks that
                                   # are the start of the paths (string, optional)
-name <path_adjust_group_name>     # The name of the path adjust group
                                   # (string, required)
-through <through_list>            # List of pins or instances where the paths
                                   # go through (string, optional)
-to <to_list>                      # List of pins, instances, or clocks where
                                   # the path ends (string, optional)